~ Hapus folder
sudo rm -rf myfolder

~ Ubah permisi folder ke siapapun bisa akses
sudo chmod -R ugo+rw /DATA/SHARE
Source https://www.linux.com/training-tutorials/how-manage-file-and-folder-permissions-linux/


Device Manager
~ cek device di usb
lsusb

~cek com port tty
ls /dev/tty*


~Cek Suhu
/usr/bin/vcgencmd measure_temp


